caption.p: Comparing the SCR among IFITM3 rs12252-CC, CT, and TT genotypes carriers after TIV vaccination from 2009 to 2015. (a) Distribution about IFITM3 rs12252-CC, CT, and TT in enrolled 212 volunteers. (b) The SCRs to H1N1, H3N2 and B/Victoria in donors with rs12252-CC, CT, and TT genotypes. (c, d) The HI antibody anti-H1N1, H3N2 and B virus were detected at baseline before influenza vaccination (c) and at day 28 after influenza immunization (d).
